{"/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_queenofspades_ver01/data/sn83045462/00280608737/1958032301/0719.xml":{"full_text":"Walk\nYour Way j\nRecovery\nToday a patient spends half the post-operative\ntime in the hospital that his parents did.\nThe reason goes back to a surprising wartime discovery\nIt's time you started moving. Come, now,\nroil over so we can get you out of bed. You're\ngoing for a walk.\" My protests to the nurse were\nof no avail. The surgeon had ordered that I\nwalk, and walk 1 would whether 1 liked it or not.\nThat was my introduction to \u201cearly ambula\ntion\" from the patient's side \u2014while 1 was\nstill groggy from the anesthetic after a major\nabdominal operation. But when you realize\nwhy surgeons demand early ambulation\none of the most important and little-heralded\nmodern medical advances it helps you bear\nthe discomfort.\nAs recently as IS years ago, a patient who\nhad his appendix out stayed in bed for ten\ndays. Surgeons believed the wound would\nopen if be moved sooner. When he finally did\nget up, he usually didn\u2019t have the strength to\nwalk across the room. Today an appendec\ntomy patient gets out of bed the first day. goes\nhome the fifth! Maternity patients also, are\nurged to get up much sooner than they used\nto be.\nThis medical innovation came about during\nWorld War 11. Doctors noticed that getting\nwo\u2014ded men np oat of bed early act\u2014lly\nhastened recovery. These area had fewer\ncomplications and less emotional frustration,\naad returned to doty sooner than patients\nconfined to their beds. Hospital bed and nurse\nshortages encouraged early ambulation. Now\nit has proved its value to all surgical patients.\nWhy should walking hasten recovery? Physi\nologists point out that when one is hurt,\nby violence or surgery, the small blood\nvessels near the injury dilate. But blood\nvessels in other areas constrict, and the\ncirculation slows. Blood cells settle out\nand tend to form clots. Air exchange in\n\u25a0y DONALD A. DUKILOW, m.d.\nBureau of Health Education\nAmerican Medical Association\nAutherlm*\nthe lungs is reduced, the kidneys become slug\ngish in removing wastes, and the digestive\nsystem goes on a strike. The whole delicate\nbalance of normal' body function becomes\nquite upset, and lying in bed keeps it upset.\nHowever, standing and walking stimulate\nthe whole circulation, and one's breathing,\ndigestion and elimination are returned to nor\nmal more quickly. In each case where patients\nwalked within hours of surgery they gained\nstrength more quickly, body functions re\nturned to normal sooner, mental attitude was\nbetter, the risk of blood dots was reduced,\nwounds healed faster, and the early walkers\ncould get back on the job long before those\nwho had had the traditional ten days in bed.\nHeart Patients, Too\nThe \u201cstroke of paralysis\" or cerebral vascu\nlar accident so often seen in older people also\nresponds quite well to early ambulation. One\nrehabilitation center reports that of patients\nstarted on an active physical medicine pro\ngram within a week of their stroke, 88 per cent\nwalked independently in an average of 30\ndays. Some doctors even encourage heart\nattack victims, traditionally kept entirely quiet,\nto get limited exercise within a week of their\nattack.\nEarly ambulation not only hastens recovery.\nA large group of pre-1938 surgical patients has\nbeen compared with a similar group who got\nthe \u201cearly ambulation\" treatment. The second\ngroup needed less than half the hospital\ntime of the first, a considerable saving at\npresent day costs.\nAnd that's just one more good reason\nto follow the nurse's orders to \u201cwalk\nwhile it still hurts.\"\n\"-How use\nMurine to rest my eyes\nafter a day outdoors*\n\u201cI have good eyes, but they usually smart after a day in a\ndusty arena,\u201d says Jim Shoulders. \u201cMurine really helps make\nmy eyes feel clean and clear again.\u201d Good tip to remember\nwhen outdoor exposure or work tension irritates your eyes.\nMurine cleanses and soothes gently.\nUse Murine morning and evening. jn\nGives your eyes real comfort. JBHJJHBI.'\u2019\"\nFOR YOUR \u00a3Y\u00a3S\u201c\nThe Murmc Co, Inc Chicago. U.S.A. \"Trademarks Reg. U. S. Pal. Off.\nAs Hi# United Natioas worts aar cheats\nfar paaca becomes greater aad greater.\nSweeten your coffee a\nwith Sucaryl* if J\nYou save all sugar\u2019s calories, and you can't taste the difference!\n\u2022Sucaryl Nm-Cmhrir XwrMrsrr, AM** ...M mk of Jrmg ttorrt rurry-wkenr jL\n15","height":"16409","width":"13227"}}
